Text:
This would be great, but 104 GB?  I'll have to pick and choose - I don't have that much room anymore.  

Thank you, though.

It's a shame this one is dead.  There was a lot of great videos here, but no one to seed.  I think the huge up scared off a lot of people.  

If this could be broken down (yes I KNOW it's individual files already) but smaller up's would entice more people to participate.  And you also have to seed for a bit!  

Other wise, sad to say, gotta pronounce it. . . time of death is. . . . .
